e Pembridge于1260年出生在英国英格兰史洛普爾卡斯特萊-普爾維爾巴时，她的父亲Ralph de Pembridge II32岁，母亲Lucy de Guildford28岁。她于1276年与Sir John de Burley Earl of Broomcroft结婚。他们至少是1个儿子和1个女儿的父母。她去世于1303年在英国英格兰賀福爾享年43岁。"},"hr":{"1260–1303":"1260.–1303.","1263–Male":"1263–preminuo","1252–Male":"1252–preminuo","1280–1358":"1280.–1358","1280–Female":"1280.–preminula","1228–Male":"1228–preminuo","1232–Female":"1232–preminula","1228":"1228","about 1280":"oko 1280.","1303":"1303.","1358":"1358","1276":"1276.","1232":"1232","1252":"1252","1263":"1263","1260":"1260.","1280":"1280.","Burley, Herefordshire, England":"Herefordshire, Engleska, United Kingdom","Bromscroft Castle, Shropshire, England":"Castle-Pulverbatch, Shropshire, Engleska, United Kingdom","England":"England","Craven Arms, Shropshire, England":"Craven Arms, Shropshire, England"},"cs":{"1260–1303":"1260–1303","1263–Male":"1263–Zesnulý","1252–Male":"1252–Zesnulý","1280–1358":"1280–1358","1280–Female":"1280–Zesnulá","1228–Male":"1228–Zesnulý","1232–Female":"1232–Zesnulá","1228":"1228","about 1280":"okolo 1280","1303":"1303","1358":"1358","1276":"1276","1232":"1232","1252":"1252","1263":"1263","1260":"1260","1280":"1280","Burley, Herefordshire, England":"Herefordshire, Anglie, United Kingdom","Bromscroft Castle, Shropshire, England":"Castle-Pulverbatch, Shropshire, Anglie, United Kingdom","England":"Anglie","Craven Arms, Shropshire, England":"Craven Arms, Shropshire, Anglie"},"da":{"1260–1303":"1260–1303","1263–Male":"1263–Afdød","1252–Male":"1252–Afdød","1280–1358":"1280–1358","1280–Female":"1280–Afdød","1228–Male":"1228–Afdød","1232–Female":"1232–Afdød","1228":"1228","about 1280":"omkring 1280","1303":"1303","1358":"1358","1276":"1276","1232":"1232","1252":"1252","1263":"1263","1260":"1260","1280":"1280","Burley, Herefordshire, England":"Herefordshire, England, United Kingdom","Bromscroft Castle, Shropshire, England":"Castle-Pulverbatch, Shropshire, England, United Kingdom","England":"England","Craven Arms, Shropshire, England":"Craven Arms, Shrop